title: DAZ3D ~ Poser : Snow Day for Autumn Picnic [DAZ 17434]
description:
--- Previously uploaded by me to KAT ---

Turn fall into winter with this snow filled texture add on pack for Autumn Picnic. This set requires that you have Autumn Picnic installed in your Runtime. It also comes with two additional props which can be added to your white, wintery renders. Snow Day is portrayed here as a contemporary setup, but the versatility of this design means it can be used for a variety of themes.

Note: The background used in the promo renders is for demonstration purposes only and is not distributed with this pack.
